      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="target">Target</h2>

<p>Typeset ‘é’ with in $\rm \LaTeX$.</p>

<p><img src="/images/posts/TypesetAccents/target.jpg" alt="target" /></p>

<!-- more -->

<h2 id="problem">Problem</h2>

<p><img src="/images/posts/TypesetAccents/problem.jpg" alt="failed" /></p>

<p><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>A failed attempt </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
